        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 24 at 3:01PM MDT by NWS Cheyenne WY</headline>
        <description>At 301 PM MDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm over
Veteran, or 13 miles southwest of Torrington, moving northeast at 25
mph.

HAZARD...Half inch hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor hail damage to vegetation is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Torrington, Yoder, Henry, Huntley, Southern Hills Estates, Torrington
Municipal Airport, Veteran, and Goshen County Fairgrounds.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
